We recommended that the Management:  

Create a committee to conduct a comprehensive physical inventory of all properties of LGU-Tumauini and prepare the necessary Report on the Physical Count of PPE to establish existence and validity; 
Maintain Property Ledger Card/Property Cards update adequate accounting and property records and conduct periodic reconciliation between accounting and property records;
Exert efforts to locate all properties and records and conduct a thorough physical check and inventory of all properties. All unserviceable properties should be properly reported to serve as basis for dropping in the books of accounts by the Accounting Department; and
Ensure strict adherence to the applicable laws, rules and regulations on PPE to prevent the incurrence of the deficiencies noted.

